
Aura Inc — Game Design Document

Overview

Aura Inc is a Roblox idle/clicker game inspired by Egg Inc. Players tap and hold to produce glowing auras that fall into habitats (storage pits). Each aura has a chance to mutate, gaining RNG-driven rarity tiers that multiply its sell value. When habitats fill up, trucks and trains haul auras to a delivery zone, converting them into currency. Players spend that currency on research upgrades, better habitats, and eventually prestige for soul-based multipliers.

Core Loop

Click/Hold → Produce auras → They fall into habitats
Habitats fill → Truck/train departs → Currency earned
Spend currency → Buy research upgrades → Produce faster/better auras
Prestige → Reset with Soul Egg multiplier → Everything scales higher

