Economy & Upgrades

Research Tree (Phase 1 Upgrades)

Aura Drop Rate — +0.5 auras/sec per level (cost scales x2.5)
Block Value — +20% base aura value per level
Block Size — Increases aura physical size (aesthetic + small value buff)
Habitat Capacity — +10% storage per level
Auto-Shipper — Reduces truck turnaround time

Prestige System (Soul Auras)

On prestige, player earns Soul Auras based on total earnings
Formula: Soul Auras = floor(0.1 * totalEarnings ^ 0.14)
Each Soul Aura = +10% permanent multiplier to all production
Players keep: Soul Auras, prestige count, any purchased Prestige Upgrades
Players reset: regular currency, research levels, habitat fill

