Egg Inc Reference — Mechanics for Aura Inc

This document is a cleaned, condensed reference of Egg Inc mechanics relevant to Aura Inc development. Use this to inform design decisions without needing to re-read the full wiki.

Boosts System

Temporary purchasable bonuses activated by the player. Core to late-game engagement and the prestige loop.

Boost Types (Egg Inc)


Critical Boost Rules (from wiki)

Max 2 boosts active at once by default (Pro Permit expands to 5)
Boost Beacons stack ADDITIVELY, not multiplicatively
Bird Feed, Prisms, and Soul Beacons do NOT compound with themselves (2x Bird Feed = 100x earnings, not 2500x)
Soul Beacons multiply the INPUT to the Soul Egg formula, not the output directly — real effect at 5x is ~1.40x actual SE gain (0.21 exponent)
Boosts cannot be activated in Contracts
Boosts can be cancelled but are NOT refunded
Buying a boost adds 25 GE to the Piggy Bank

Aura Inc Equivalents Planned (Phase 3)


Prestige System

Soul Egg Formula (Egg Inc)

SoulEggs = floor(totalBocks^0.21 * constant)

Aura Inc Version (confirmed Phase 2)

NewSoulAuras = floor(totalEarned^0.25 * 0.14)

The exponent difference (0.21 vs 0.25) makes Aura Inc prestige slightly more rewarding per run at mid-game ranges, which fits the faster-paced Roblox session length.

What Resets vs Survives (Egg Inc pattern — Aura Inc mirrors this)


Eggs of Prophecy (Aura Inc: Prophecy Auras — Phase 3/4)

Exponential multiplier on top of soul egg bonus
Egg Inc formula: EarningsBonus = (1 + SA_bonus) ^ EoP_count
These are the "end game chase" — extremely hard to get, insane payoff
Aura Inc: Save for Phase 3/4, do not implement in Phase 3 unless time allows

Research System

Egg Inc Structure

Tier 1 (Common Research) — cheap, many levels, resets on prestige. Examples: Comfortable Nests, Nutritional Supplements, Better Incubators
Tier 2 (Epic Research) — expensive (Golden Eggs), permanent across prestiges, few levels. Examples: Epic Hatchery, Soul Food, Prestige Bonus
Each tier has ~15-20 research items across categories

Key Epic Research items relevant to Aura Inc


Aura Inc Research Plan (Phase 3)

Common Research (resets on prestige): Block Value, Habitat Size, Hatchery Size, Mutation Speed, Passive Tick — ALREADY BUILT
Epic Research (permanent): Phase 3 flagship — tier ceiling unlocks, permanent SA bonus, hatchery permanents
