Challenges (Egg Inc) → Tier Collection Challenges (Aura Inc)

Egg Inc Pattern

Challenges are in-game quests that reward Bocks, Soul Eggs, or Golden Eggs
Examples: "Research 30 things", "Lay eggs worth $300,000", "75K chickens"
