Drones (Egg Inc — NOT planned for Aura Inc)

Golden Egg tap rewards from flying drones. Not equivalent to any Aura Inc mechanic. Could be a Phase 4 "bonus tap event" but no plans currently.

Spaceships / Artifacts / Eggfinity Stones (NOT planned)

Full late-game system for Egg Inc. Too complex and too different from Aura Inc's identity. Not in scope for any current phase.

